  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are a veteran hunter.</h2> When you return home, things are not going well and you realize that there is no one left in your town. You realize from the shadows that a mysterious creature is following you. You dive deep into the town and forest to track it down.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A lot of things in town are broken or out of power. </h2>You must try to fix them in order to solve various mysteries and gain an advantage against the creature.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't forget that when you come face to face with the creature.</h2> It can kill you in one strike. You can use objects like traps and guns to scare the it.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There are multiple endings in the game.</h2> Each time you start a game, the creature's behavior changes according to your actions. You can have a different experience every time you play.",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/1cbc0adc6bb24844e620300b72189461.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are a veteran hunter.</h2> When you return home, things are not going well and you realize that there is no one left in your town. You realize from the shadows that a mysterious creature is following you. You dive deep into the town and forest to track it down.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/4fbc9be5e6051c349cbadb854684ac76.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A lot of things in town are broken or out of power. </h2>You must try to fix them in order to solve various mysteries and gain an advantage against the creature.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/44c18f317dc9e3b9a416c9ed7297324d.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't forget that when you come face to face with the creature.</h2> It can kill you in one strike. You can use objects like traps and guns to scare the it.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.poster.avif?t=1698248281\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.webm?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444840/extras/b1003391ac014c79e626f94203ca71de.mp4?t=1698248281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There are multiple endings in the game.</h2> Each time you start a game, the creature's behavior changes according to your actions. You can have a different experience every time you play.",
